data.name: UpsertMtaStsEntity
data.value: INSERT INTO `mtasts_entity` (`id`, `version`, `state`) VALUES (@domain, @version, @state) ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE state = IF(version < @version, VALUES(state), state), version = IF(version < @version, VALUES(version), version);

data.name: SelectMtaStsEntity
data.value: SELECT state FROM mtasts_entity WHERE id = @domain ORDER BY version DESC LIMIT 1;
